<style>
  .shopify-section-group-header-group,.shopify-section-group-footer-group{display:none!important}
  .ele-page{font-family:Georgia,"Times New Roman",Times,serif;background:#f7f5f2;color:#1a1a1a}.ele-page *{box-sizing:border-box}.ele-wrap{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:70px 22px}.ele-kicker{color:#2D5016;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.12em;font-weight:800;font-size:13px}.ele-page h1{font-size:clamp(42px,7vw,82px);line-height:.95;letter-spacing:-.06em;margin:14px 0 20px}.ele-page h2{font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,52px);line-height:1;letter-spacing:-.045em;margin:0 0 16px}.ele-page p{font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;color:#3a3a3a}.ele-split{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:28px;align-items:center;margin-top:30px}.ele-img{min-height:430px;border-radius:28px;overflow:hidden;background:#e8e0d5}.ele-img img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block}.ele-card{background:white;border:1px solid #e5dfd6;border-radius:28px;padding:34px;box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(17,17,17,.06)}@media(max-width:780px){.ele-split{grid-template-columns:1fr}.ele-img{min-height:300px}.ele-wrap{padding:46px 18px}}
</style>
<main class="ele-page">
  <section class="ele-wrap">
    <span class="ele-kicker">Our Mission & Foundation</span>
    <h1>More Than a Sanctuary. Their Lifelong Safe Haven.</h1>
    <p>Founded in 2016, we began our journey after witnessing the heartbreaking cruelty elephants faced in the tourism industry. Today, as a legally registered Elephant Welfare Foundation in Thailand, we proudly protect 20+ rescued elephants across our sanctuaries, giving them the untamed freedom they deserve.</p>
    <div class="ele-split">
      <div class="ele-img"><img src="{{ 'elehub-selected-016.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Elephants walking freely in a forest sanctuary" width="1200" height="850" loading="lazy"></div>
      <div class="ele-card"><h2>Thaielehub: Where Elephants Meet the Horizon</h2><p>Thaielehub practices sustainable agriculture, natural forest habitat, and quiet respect. We grow food for the herd, protect the land around them, and reject riding, performances, and forced bathing. Every encounter begins with one principle: the elephant's choice comes first.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="ele-split">
      <div class="ele-card"><h2>Thaielehub: Where Ethical Encounters Meet Untamed Freedom</h2><p>Thaielehub follows a strict no-control, observation-first philosophy. Across more than 40 acres of natural habitat, the sanctuary supports veterinary care, forest restoration, and anti-exploitation education while allowing elephants to live with dignity and wild rhythm.</p></div>
      <div class="ele-img"><img src="{{ 'elehub-selected-009.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Thaielehub elephants in natural sanctuary habitat" width="1200" height="850" loading="lazy"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
{% schema %}{"name":"Elephant mission page","settings":[],"presets":[{"name":"Elephant mission page"}]}{% endschema %}
